 CREATE TABLE Sections (section_id number, course_id number, section_name text, section_description text, other_details text, PRIMARY KEY(section_id), FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES Courses(course_id))

 CREATE TABLE Student_Enrolment_Courses (student_course_id number, course_id number, student_enrolment_id number, PRIMARY KEY(student_course_id), FOREIGN KEY (student_enrolment_id) REFERENCES Student_Enrolment(student_enrolment_id), FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES Courses(course_id)) 
 CREATE TABLE Transcripts (transcript_id number, transcript_date time, other_details text, PRIMARY KEY(transcript_id)) 
 CREATE TABLE Transcript_Contents (student_course_id number, transcript_id number, FOREIGN KEY (transcript_id) REFERENCES Transcripts(transcript_id), FOREIGN KEY (student_course_id) REFERENCES Student_Enrolment_Courses(student_course_id))
